<span id="freeTextContainer4764238761501795198">A.K.A. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/47687.Barbara_Vine' title='Barbara Vine' rel='nofollow noopener'>Barbara Vine</a><br/><br/>Ruth Barbara Rendell, Baroness Rendell of Babergh, CBE, who also wrote under the pseudonym <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/47687.Barbara_Vine' title='Barbara Vine' rel='nofollow noopener'>Barbara Vine</a>, was an acclaimed English crime writer, known for her many psychological thrillers and murder mysteries and above all for Inspector Wexford.</span>
  <span id="freeText4764238761501795198" style="display:none">A.K.A. <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/47687.Barbara_Vine" title="Barbara Vine" rel="nofollow noopener">Barbara Vine</a><br /><br />Ruth Barbara Rendell, Baroness Rendell of Babergh, CBE, who also wrote under the pseudonym <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/47687.Barbara_Vine" title="Barbara Vine" rel="nofollow noopener">Barbara Vine</a>, was an acclaimed English crime writer, known for her many psychological thrillers and murder mysteries and above all for Inspector Wexford.</span>
